consensus text: The filter for N[superscript]o[/superscript] 1 weighs 76 Grs gains [deletion]26[/deletion] [insertion]7[/insertion] Grs [unclear]128 83 in all
Chromate of [deletion]Lead[/deletion] obtained from that of Iron
by fusion with 3 times its weight of [deletion]S[/deletion] carb Kali
then saturated & with a slight [insertion][unclear]P[/unclear][/insertion] excess of Nitric acid
it requires a strong heat for 10 minutes and not to
